## Mengakses Dataset
```{r pressure, echo=FALSE}
df<- read.csv("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/yulandariarsyad/Pusat-Studi-Data-Sains-UAD/main/Data",stringsAsFactors = T)
head(df)
```
###Scatter Plot Data
```{r}
library(ggplot2)

ggplot(df, aes(x=Total.Salary,y=Total.Compensation))+
  geom_point()
```
###Membangun model Regresi Linear
```{r}
ggplot(df, aes(x=Total.Salary,y=Total.Compensation))+
  geom_point()+geom_smooth(method='lm',se=T)
```
